						<p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Generally, you may be eligible if you have a BMI over 40, or a BMI over 35 with obesity-related health conditions such as type 2 diabetes, high blood pressure, or sleep apnoea. Your surgeon will assess your individual circumstances during consultation.</p>
					</details>

					<details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 group">
