						<p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Costs vary depending on the procedure and your circumstances. With private health insurance, out-of-pocket costs typically range from $5,000-$12,000. Without insurance, full costs range from $15,000-$30,000. Medicare rebates may apply. Use our cost calculator for a personalised estimate.</p>
