						<p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Most patients stay in hospital for 1-2 nights and can return to light activities within 1-2 weeks. Full recovery typically takes 4-6 weeks. Your surgeon will provide specific guidelines based on your procedure and individual healing.</p>
