						<p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Modern weight loss surgery is generally safe when performed by experienced surgeons. Serious complications occur in less than 5% of cases. Your surgeon will discuss specific risks during consultation. The long-term health benefits often outweigh the surgical risks for eligible patients.</p>
