						<p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Yes, Medicare provides rebates for weight loss surgery if you meet eligibility criteria. However, Medicare only covers a portion of the costs. Private health insurance with appropriate hospital and extras cover can significantly reduce your out-of-pocket expenses.</p>
